trans-unit.source: Contains all of the cached data objects that are declared in a single class in a document-level customization that was created by using the Office development tools in Visual Studio.
trans-unit.target: 包含文档级自定义的单个类中声明的所有缓存数据对象，该文档级自定义通过使用 Visual Studio 中的 Office 开发工具创建。

trans-unit.source: For more information about caching data in document-level customizations, see [Caching Data](/visualstudio/vsto/caching-data.md) and [Accessing Data in Documents on the Server](/visualstudio/vsto/accessing-data-in-documents-on-the-server.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关在文档级自定义项中缓存数据的详细信息，请参阅[缓存数据](/visualstudio/vsto/caching-data.md)和[访问的服务器上的文档数据](/visualstudio/vsto/accessing-data-in-documents-on-the-server.md)。

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of cached data objects that are declared in a single class in an Office solution.
trans-unit.target: 获取在 Office 解决方案中的单个类中声明的缓存数据对象的集合。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItemCollection" /> that contains the cached data objects that are declared in a single class in an Office solution.
trans-unit.target: A <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataItemCollection" /> ，包含在 Office 解决方案中的单个类中声明的缓存的数据对象。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the namespace and class in which the cached data objects in the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataHostItem" /> are declared.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置命名空间和类，其中已声明 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataHostItem" /> 中的缓存数据对象。

trans-unit.source: The namespace and class in which the cached data objects in the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataHostItem" /> are declared.
trans-unit.target: 命名空间和缓存的数据中的对象的类<see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataHostItem" />声明。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataHostItem.Id%2A> property is a string that specifies the namespace and the class separated by a ".", for example, "ExcelWorkbook1.ThisWorkbook".
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataHostItem.Id%2A>属性是一个字符串，指定命名空间和隔开的类"。"，例如，"ExcelWorkbook1.ThisWorkbook"。
